           add       1                    to   w-all-str-inx          .
           if        w-all-str-inx        >    26
                     go to acc-pwd-ute-chk-400.

           if        w-acc-pwd-ute-chk    =    w-all-str-loc
                                              (w-all-str-inx)
                     add   1              to   w-acc-pwd-ute-cmi
                     go to acc-pwd-ute-chk-400.
           go to     acc-pwd-ute-chk-220.
