      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       rou-let-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione status di uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-rou-let-reg      .
       rou-let-reg-010.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura record personalizzazioni generali       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RD"                 to   j-ope                  .
           move      "PSG "               to   j-tre                  .
           move      spaces               to   j-kre                  .
