      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       pre-acc-ins-110.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-dup-rec-flg    =    spaces
                     go to pre-acc-ins-200.
       pre-acc-ins-120.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
