      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-ute-cod-ute        to   w-clo-ute-cod-ute      .
           move      w-clo-ute-rec-ute    to   w-ute                  .
           move      w-clo-ute-cod-ute    to   w-ute-cod-ute          .
       pre-acc-ins-132.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura codice stampante per descrizione    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-ute-cst-ass        to   w-let-arc-stp-cod      .
